To install:

1. Go to the directory where you want the to install to
2. git clone git://github.com/tareko/Kitab-Al-Shifa.git kitab
   (you can choose another name then kitab if you like)
3. cd kitab
4. mkdir app/webroot/pdf
5. Either
	a. chown www-data.www-data app/webroot/pdf   # or
	b. chmod 777 app/webroot/pdf

6. Make sure app/tmp/ and subdirectories are writeable by the webserver

7. Config directory
8. cp app/Config/core.default.php app/Config/core.php
9. Add the kitab.sql scheme and Joomla scheme if needed
